body:
It appears Shen does have a connection to the Vastaya for this line in Xayah bio there is this line:
&quot;The haunting melodies transported her to a long-forgotten time, when the spirit realm danced freely throughout the physical world&quot; 
And feel free to correct me if I am wrong but ain&#039;t Shen kinda connected to the Spirit world (or at least his sword). I don&#039;t think it means that he is a Vastaya since this is a tradition in his family to keep them separated but might mean that Shen and Xayah might be in odds no?
